The two OH Assist charges make up one monthly invoice received in the total sum of 99450.31 (gross inc VAT) in relation to outsourced contract provision of a full range of occupational health services. Service includes menu of core provision plus bespoke/project based interventions to support HMRC stratgey to reduce Average Working Days Lost due to sickness absence. Service also includes vaccinations and pre-posting health checks supporting health risk management strategies and duty of care.
